SmartThings NG will be configured to send push updates to Home Assistant at:
> {webhook_url}

If this is not correct, please update your configuration, restart Home Assistant, and try again.

abort.invalid_webhook_url:
Home Assistant is not configured correctly to receive updates from SmartThings. The webhook URL is invalid:
> {webhook_url}

Please update your configuration per the [instructions]({component_url}), restart Home Assistant, and try again.
